  customer: { yearsWithMHPCO: 0 },
  steps: [{ op: "quote", items: [] }]
}) => { results: [{ premium: 5 }] }
```

The simplest implementation is to just return `{ results: [{ premium: 5 }] }` regardless of input. This is a hardcoded return that passes the current test.

